    "shortDescription": "<p>You preserve the remains of a dead creature so that they do not decay. Doing so effectively extends the time limit on raising that creature from the dead (see <i>raise dead</i>). Days spent under the influence of this spell don't count against the time limit.</p><p>Additionally, this spell makes transporting a slain (and thus decaying) comrade less unpleasant.</p><p>The spell also works on severed body parts and the like.</p>"
